{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/simple-theme-tutorial-collection-list-title-below-image","result":{"pageContext":{"id":1074,"date":"2021-07-27T03:25:06","date_gmt":"2021-07-27T03:25:06","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=1074"},"modified":"2021-08-12T00:43:08","modified_gmt":"2021-08-12T00:43:08","slug":"simple-theme-tutorial-collection-list-title-below-image","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/simple-theme-tutorial-collection-list-title-below-image/","title":{"rendered":"Simple &#038; Debut theme: show &#8220;collection list&#8221; section&#8217;s title below the image"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>In this tutorial I&#8217;ll quickly teach you how to move your &#8220;collection list&#8221; section&#8217;s title right below the collection image.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-adding-the-css-code\">Adding the CSS code</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>From your Shopify admin, navigate to <strong>online store &gt; themes &gt; actions &gt; edit code.</strong><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1349\" height=\"614\" class=\"wp-image-626\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code.jpg 1349w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code-600x273.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code-1200x546.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code-768x350.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1349px) 100vw, 1349px\" /><br></li><li>Locate the file named <strong>theme.scss</strong> or <strong>theme.css</strong> and add the following code at the bottom of the file:<br><br>[gist]9a254d24b536e50dc88db0f04d791d0d[gist]<br></li><li>Click &#8220;save&#8221; at the top right corner. It should look like this:<br></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"846\" height=\"725\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/image-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1075\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/image-1.png 846w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/image-1-768x658.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 846px) 100vw, 846px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can modify the value <strong>35px</strong> to increase the bottom spacing. You can also change the text&#8217;s color by replacing <strong>#000000</strong> with any HEX color of your wish.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Using the Debut theme?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Make your store stand out of the crowd with our other tutorials:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/debut-shopify-theme-how-to-add-swipe-for-product-page-images\" target=\"_blank\">Add swipe/arrows to your product page images</a></li><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/debut-theme-sticky-navigation-bar-tutorial\" target=\"_blank\">Sticky navigation bar (plus 20+ customizable features)</a></li><li><a data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/show-second-image-on-hover-debut-theme\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/show-second-image-on-hover-debut-theme\" target=\"_blank\">Show second image on hover</a></li><li><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/debut-theme-product-page-images-zoom-tutorial\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8220;Click to zoom&#8221; lightbox for product page images</a></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-container-621e5dca2b866 wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"></div></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some other Debut tutorials you may be interested in:<br><br>&#8211; <a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/debut-shopify-theme-how-to-add-swipe-for-product-page-images\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Add arrows to the product page images;</a><br>&#8211; <a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/debut-theme-product-page-images-zoom-tutorial\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Add a &#8220;click to zoom&#8221; on mobile &amp; desktop for product page images.</a><br>&#8211; <a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/debut-theme-sticky-navigation-bar-tutorial\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sticky header</a></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Simple CSS code to move the collection&#8217;s title from inside of the image to below the image. Works on both the Simple and Debut theme.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1082,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[154,157,384],"image_alt":"","acf":[],"featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/simple_theme_2-850x478.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/simple_theme_2-200x200.png","featured_image_large_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/simple_theme_2-1200x675.png","post_count":null,"categories_names":["Blog"],"tag_names":["Code Tutorial","debut theme","simple theme"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1074"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/users/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/comments?post=1074"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1074/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1113,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1074/revisions/1113"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media/1082"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media?parent=1074"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/categories?post=1074"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddabl